---
import Layout from '@/layouts/Layout.astro';
import Footer from '@/components/layout/Footer.astro';

---

<Layout>

	<main class="min-h-screen text-slate-950" style="background-color: var(--color-bg)">
		<div class="px-4 md:px-10">
			
		</div>
		<section class="mx-auto max-w-3xl px-6 py-16 sm:px-10">
			<div class="rounded-3xl border border-slate-200 bg-white/90 p-10 shadow-xl shadow-slate-900/5 backdrop-blur">
				<h1 class="text-4xl font-semibold tracking-tight text-slate-950 sm:text-5xl">Affiliate Disclosure & Sponsored Content Policy</h1>
				<p class="mt-4 text-sm text-slate-500">Last updated: June 2026</p>

				<h2 class="mt-10 text-2xl font-semibold tracking-tight text-slate-950">1. Introduction</h2>
				<p class="mt-4 leading-7 text-slate-600">Transparency and trust are important values at Voyaflair.</p>
				<p class="mt-3 leading-7 text-slate-600">
					This page explains how affiliate relationships, sponsored content, gifted experiences, media stays, press trips, and other forms of compensation may be used on this website.
				</p>
				<p class="mt-3 leading-7 text-slate-600">
					Our goal is to provide honest, useful, and authentic travel content while being transparent about any relationships with brands, tourism boards, hotels, travel companies, or service providers.
				</p>

				<h2 class="mt-8 text-2xl font-semibold tracking-tight text-slate-950">2. Affiliate Links</h2>
				<p class="mt-4 leading-7 text-slate-600">
					Some articles, guides, newsletters, emails, and other content published on Voyaflair may contain affiliate links.
				</p>
				<p class="mt-3 leading-7 text-slate-600">
					If you click on an affiliate link and make a purchase, booking, registration, or other qualifying action, Voyaflair may earn a commission.
				</p>
				<p class="mt-3 leading-7 text-slate-600">This comes at no additional cost to you.</p>
				<p class="mt-3 leading-7 text-slate-600">The price you pay remains the same whether you use an affiliate link or not.</p>
				<p class="mt-3 leading-7 text-slate-600">
					Affiliate commissions help support the operation, maintenance, and continued creation of content on Voyaflair.
				</p>

				<h2 class="mt-8 text-2xl font-semibold tracking-tight text-slate-950">3. Affiliate Programs</h2>
				<p class="mt-4 leading-7 text-slate-600">
					Voyaflair may participate in various affiliate programs related to travel, including but not limited to:
				</p>
				<ul class="mt-3 list-disc space-y-1 pl-6 text-slate-600">
					<li>Accommodation booking platforms</li>
					<li>Tour and activity providers</li>
					<li>Travel insurance providers</li>
					<li>Travel gear and accessories</li>
					<li>Software and digital services</li>
					<li>Transportation providers</li>
					<li>Other travel-related products and services</li>
				</ul>
				<p class="mt-3 leading-7 text-slate-600">Affiliate partnerships may change over time.</p>

				<h2 class="mt-8 text-2xl font-semibold tracking-tight text-slate-950">4. Editorial Independence</h2>
				<p class="mt-4 leading-7 text-slate-600">
					Affiliate relationships do not influence our opinions, recommendations, or reviews.
				</p>
				<p class="mt-3 leading-7 text-slate-600">
					We strive to provide honest and unbiased information regardless of whether compensation is involved.
				</p>
				<p class="mt-3 leading-7 text-slate-600">
					The existence of an affiliate relationship does not guarantee a positive review or recommendation.
				</p>

				<h2 class="mt-8 text-2xl font-semibold tracking-tight text-slate-950">5. Sponsored Content</h2>
				<p class="mt-4 leading-7 text-slate-600">From time to time, Voyaflair may publish sponsored content.</p>
				<p class="mt-3 leading-7 text-slate-600">Sponsored content may include:</p>
				<ul class="mt-3 list-disc space-y-1 pl-6 text-slate-600">
					<li>Sponsored blog posts</li>
					<li>Brand collaborations</li>
					<li>Paid partnerships</li>
					<li>Sponsored social media campaigns</li>
					<li>Sponsored destination features</li>
					<li>Sponsored travel experiences</li>
				</ul>
				<p class="mt-3 leading-7 text-slate-600">
					Whenever content is sponsored, we will make reasonable efforts to clearly disclose that relationship.
				</p>

				<h2 class="mt-8 text-2xl font-semibold tracking-tight text-slate-950">6. Gifted Experiences and Complimentary Services</h2>
				<p class="mt-4 leading-7 text-slate-600">
					Voyaflair may occasionally receive complimentary products, services, experiences, accommodation, transportation, meals, tours, event access, or other benefits.
				</p>
				<p class="mt-3 leading-7 text-slate-600">Examples may include:</p>
				<ul class="mt-3 list-disc space-y-1 pl-6 text-slate-600">
					<li>Hotel stays</li>
					<li>Resort stays</li>
					<li>Guided tours</li>
					<li>Travel experiences</li>
					<li>Attraction tickets</li>
					<li>Restaurant invitations</li>
					<li>Travel products</li>
				</ul>
				<p class="mt-3 leading-7 text-slate-600">Receiving complimentary products or services does not guarantee positive coverage.</p>
				<p class="mt-3 leading-7 text-slate-600">Opinions expressed remain our own.</p>

				<h2 class="mt-8 text-2xl font-semibold tracking-tight text-slate-950">7. Media Stays and Press Trips</h2>
				<p class="mt-4 leading-7 text-slate-600">
					Voyaflair may participate in media stays, familiarization trips (FAM trips), press trips, or tourism board collaborations.
				</p>
				<p class="mt-3 leading-7 text-slate-600">
					These opportunities may involve partial or full coverage of travel-related expenses.
				</p>
				<p class="mt-3 leading-7 text-slate-600">
					Content created during such collaborations will continue to reflect our genuine experiences and opinions.
				</p>
				<p class="mt-3 leading-7 text-slate-600">Where appropriate, these collaborations will be disclosed.</p>

				<h2 class="mt-8 text-2xl font-semibold tracking-tight text-slate-950">8. Advertising</h2>
				<p class="mt-4 leading-7 text-slate-600">
					Voyaflair may display advertisements from third-party advertising networks.
				</p>
				<p class="mt-3 leading-7 text-slate-600">
					Advertisements may be presented in various formats, including display ads, banner ads, native ads, and other advertising placements.
				</p>
				<p class="mt-3 leading-7 text-slate-600">
					Voyaflair is not responsible for the products, services, claims, or practices of advertisers.
				</p>

				<h2 class="mt-8 text-2xl font-semibold tracking-tight text-slate-950">9. Product Recommendations</h2>
				<p class="mt-4 leading-7 text-slate-600">
					Recommendations made on Voyaflair are based on personal experience, research, editorial judgment, or a combination of these factors.
				</p>
				<p class="mt-3 leading-7 text-slate-600">
					However, readers should always conduct their own research and make purchasing or booking decisions based on their individual needs and circumstances.
				</p>

				<h2 class="mt-8 text-2xl font-semibold tracking-tight text-slate-950">10. No Guarantees</h2>
				<p class="mt-4 leading-7 text-slate-600">
					While we aim to provide accurate and helpful recommendations, Voyaflair does not guarantee:
				</p>
				<ul class="mt-3 list-disc space-y-1 pl-6 text-slate-600">
					<li>Product performance</li>
					<li>Service quality</li>
					<li>Travel experiences</li>
					<li>Availability</li>
					<li>Pricing</li>
					<li>Booking outcomes</li>
				</ul>
				<p class="mt-3 leading-7 text-slate-600">Travel products and services may change over time.</p>
				<p class="mt-3 leading-7 text-slate-600">
					Readers are encouraged to verify information directly with providers before making decisions.
				</p>

				<h2 class="mt-8 text-2xl font-semibold tracking-tight text-slate-950">11. Contact Information</h2>
				<p class="mt-4 leading-7 text-slate-600">
					If you have any questions regarding this Affiliate Disclosure & Sponsored Content Policy, please contact:
				</p>
				<p class="mt-3 leading-7 text-slate-600">
					<a href="mailto:voyaflair@gmail.com" class="font-medium text-slate-900 underline underline-offset-4 hover:text-slate-700 text-[0.875rem]" style="font-family: Inter, system-ui, -apple-system, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, sans-serif;">voyaflair@gmail.com</a>
				</p>
			</div>
		</section>

	</main>

	<Footer />
</Layout>
